sources.description:
One man justice! Faces ruthless rustlers in a lawless frontier!
A Deputy Marshal tracks fugitive bank robbers to Wyoming, and then fights to help ranchers save their land from a railroad land scheme.

Original title: Deputy Marshal (1949)
This film is is subtitled with many language options.

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/fvflcMMamig


Director: William Berke
Writers: William Berke, Charles Heckelmann
Stars: Jon Hall, Frances Langford, Dick Foran, Russell Hayden, Julie Bishop
Genre: Colorized classics, Western, Musical
